snippet.textDisplay:
The song is amazing and everything about it is amazing other than Sara haider.  She has an amazing voice but she doesn't sing her lyrics like she actually feels them or even understands them.  She's focused on music, compared to Ali Zafar who in this song is able to do both music and feel perfectly. 

This will always be the weakness in this otherwise perfect piece.
